dct:description: Information about an individual’s friends or connections expressed as a social network
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Public Life
dct:description: Information about an individual’s public life
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Communication
dct:description: Information communicated from or to an individual
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Acquantaince
dct:description: Information about acquaintainces in a social network.
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Association
dct:description: Information about associations in a social network with other individuals, groups, or entities e.g. friend of a friend
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Connection
dct:description: Information about and including connections of an individual in a social network
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Friend
dct:description: Information about friends of the individual in a social network. Includes aspects of friendships such as years together or nature of friendship.
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Group Membership
dct:description: Information about groups the individual is included or associated with in a social network
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Device Based
dct:description: Information about a device that an individual uses for personal use (even part-time or with others)
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Location
dct:description: Information about an individual’s location
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Contact
dct:description: Information that can be used for contacting an individual e.g. email address or phone number
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Credit
dct:description: Information about an individual’s reputation with regards to money
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Income
dct:description: Information about financial income e.g. for individual or household or family
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Loan Record
dct:description: Information about loans provided or related to the individual
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Purchase
dct:description: Information about purchases such as items bought e.g. grocery or clothing
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Purchases and Spending Habit
dct:description: Information about analysis of purchases made and money spent expressed as a habit e.g. monthly shopping trends
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Sale
dct:description: Information about sales e.g. selling of goods or services
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Tax
dct:description: Information about financial tax e.g. tax records or tax due
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra

rdfs:label: Transaction
dct:description: Information about financial transactions e.g. bank transfers
dct:creator: Elmar Kiesling, Harshvardhan J. Pandit, Fajar Ekaputra
